Grandmother Anya, near the house of which in the village of Ivanovka Petrikovsky district for twenty years lives an aist family, began to notice how the nest settles, despite all the efforts of its inhabitants.
Birds put new twigs on top, and the lower layer has already flown between the wires, is about to collapse.
