As soon as the birds flew to the warm edges, Anya's grandmother called the Tsarichansky DEN, which owns the support.
I didn't even expect to react so quickly.
When our specialists arrived in Ivanovka, they were surprised that the nest is still holding, - said the technical director of DTEK "Dneprooblenergo" Sergey Berezovsky.
